item management s discussion and analysis of results of operations and financial condition general the company was founded in to provide custom programming services and  in  it began to design  develop  market and support automated business management systems for distributors  wholesalers and dealers 
the company s revenue is derived primarily from the sale of prophet systems  maintenance contracts which provide for software support and equipment maintenance and the sale of optional software products 
each prophet system includes the prophet xl software  an ibm risc system computer  various optional third party software products and hardware components  training  support and installation 
the company s cost of revenue consists principally of the costs of hardware components  customer support  installation and training and  to a lesser extent  third party software 
the company implemented a strategic decision early in to move from its internally developed proprietary hardware system to an open system platform  based on the unix aix operating system running on an ibm risc system computer 
the company s adoption of an open system solution broadened the market for the prophet system  facilitated greater customer acceptance and allowed successful integration of industry standard third party software and hardware 
the company introduced in fiscal its next generation product  prophet acclaim  a complete business management system that combines the functionality of the traditional prophet system with the technology of progress software s dbms 
prophet acclaim is targeted for sales to new and current customers 
it has been designed so that current customers can move to this new product while preserving their existing technology infrastructure 
prophet acclaim is currently in beta testing  and the company estimates that it will be generally released in the second quarter of fiscal this annual report contains forward looking statements that involve risks and uncertainties 
the company s actual results may differ materially from the results discussed in such forward looking statements 
